   | 20     | SPACE
 N | 4e     | LATIN CAPITAL LETTER N
 i | 69     | LATIN SMALL LETTER I
 ñ | f1     | LATIN SMALL LETTER N WITH TILDE
 o | 6f     | LATIN SMALL LETTER O
(7 rows)

